mg_club
==============================================================
In this map you must dance ^^.
All player can dance,chill or smoke drugs^^.
After 6 min you get a knife in the disco and must knife all.
The DJ-console is very specific.
You can choose 3 songs and 1000 light mods.
[SPECIAL]You have smoke and virtual laser.
[SPECIAL]Spotlight!
==============================================================
You must enter a password to go into the DJ-room.
The password is 85624.
==============================================================
The map is 31mb big because their are 3 songs in the map!!
Songs:
[1]:Frauenarzt "Disco pogo"
[2]:David Guetta feat " Akon - Sexy"
[3]:Black eyed peace "Meet me half way"
